name: TurboProject
overview:
TurboProject is a project management software application with three software versions to choose from. TurboProject Express is ideal for small, simple tasks and projects. TurboProject Standard provides full project control with advanced resource management, and TurboProject Professional is ideal for multiple teams and projects.

Helping to improve and manage projects, tasks, planning, and preparation from simple projects to large complex projects.
